OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FDespite agreeing to a ceasefire in
OL,7,FApril, the United States and Iran have
OL,8,Fnot yet reached a peace deal.
OL,10,FIt is not immediately clear how close
OL,11,Fthe two parties are to an agreement,
OL,12,Fwith Iranian Foreign Minister Abbas
OL,13,FAraghchi saying this week that "no
OL,14,Ftangible progress" has been made,
OL,15,Fdespite previous optimism from US
OL,16,FPresident Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
