OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780740351
OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FTrump discussed the peace talks with
OL,7,FIran during a Wednesday interview,
OL,8,Fsaying he thought it would be
OL,9,F"unlikely" that the Strait of Hormuz
OL,10,Fwould still be closed on Labor Day in
OL,11,Fthe US, which is on September 7.
OL,13,FThe US president added that Iran's
OL,14,FSupreme Leader Mojtaba Khamenei, who
OL,15,Fsucceeded his late father, is
OL,16,F"involved" in peace talks for ending
OL,17,Fthe war.
OL,19,F"They have a lot of respect for him,"
OL,20,FTrump said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
