OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FOne of the stumbling blocks to a peace
OL,7,Fdeal is Israel's war in Lebanon
OL,8,Fagainst the Iran-backed militant group
OL,9,FHezbollah.
OL,11,FIran insists that an agreement to end
OL,12,Fthe Iran-US war means an end to
OL,13,FIsraeli strikes on Lebanon.
OL,15,FFighting in the country continued on
OL,16,FFriday, as Israel's air force struck
OL,17,Fsouthern parts of Lebanon, where there
OL,18,Fis a heavy Hezbollah presence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780740351
OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FThe Israeli military issued evacuation
OL,7,Fwarnings for nine villages, and
OL,8,FLebanon's state news agency reported
OL,9,Fthat six people were killed.
OL,11,FFriday's strikes came after Hezbollah
OL,12,Frejected a ceasefire agreement,
OL,13,Fdemanding a complete Israeli
OL,14,Fwithdrawal.
OL,16,FThe war threatens efforts to end the
OL,17,FIran conflict and reopen the Strait of
OL,18,FHormuz, a critical waterway off the
OL,19,Fcoast of Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
