OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FThe Strait, which is almost 100 miles
OL,7,Flong and 21 miles wide at its
OL,8,Fnarrowest point, usually allows a
OL,9,Ffifth of global oil and gas supplies
OL,10,Fto pass through.
OL,12,FThe chokepoint has been largely
OL,13,Fblocked off by Iran since the start of
OL,14,Fthe war, following the killing of its
OL,15,Fsupreme leader, Ali Khamenei. Only a
OL,16,Fhandful of tankers are currently
OL,17,Fcrossing each day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
