OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FForeign Secretary of State Yvette
OL,7,FCooper has stressed the need to get
OL,8,F"international shipping moving"
OL,9,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz again.
OL,11,FYvette Cooper told ITV News that
OL,12,Fglobal shipping is currently being
OL,13,F"hijacked", and called on Iran to lift
OL,14,Frestrictions.
OL,16,F"Most importantly", she added, "we
OL,17,Fneed an agreement to be reached that
OL,18,Fcan allow shipping to move properly
OL,19,Fagain".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
