OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780740351
OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FThe Foreign Secretary said that
OL,7,FBritain and France have been "leading
OL,8,Fwork" around a maritime mission aimed
OL,9,Fat supporting mine clearance and
OL,10,Freassurance for shipping, once an
OL,11,Fagreement has been reached.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FAs Iran maintains its hold on the
OL,19,FStrait of Hormuz, the US continues its
OL,20,Fblockade of Iranian ports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
