OL,3,CHormuz Strait crisis deepens as Iran-
OL,4,CUS peace talks falter
OL,6,FThe US Navy has imposed a blockade of
OL,7,FIran's ports as part of an effort to
OL,8,Fforce Tehran to open the strait and
OL,9,Faccept a deal to extend a tenuous
OL,10,Fceasefire in the war.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, on Friday, US forces
OL,13,Fboarded a sanctioned oil tanker linked
OL,14,Fto the Islamic Republic in the Indian
OL,15,FOcean, the US military said.
OL,17,FUS Indo-Pacific Command posted on X
OL,18,Fthat the forces boarded the MT Davina,
OL,19,Fwithout offering details.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
